Module com.example.schedulesoft
Package com.example.schedulesoft.ui

Class AppointmentsByCountryChart

java.lang.Object
com.example.schedulesoft.ui.AppointmentsByCountryChart
public class AppointmentsByCountryChart extends Object
Creates a bar chart displaying the number of appointments associated with each country. This is a UI class that creates a UI object that can be used a re-usable component.

This is the extra report asked for in the requirements.
